  "description": "hulubul.com is a digital platform that connects the Moldovan diaspora with transporters running regular routes between the Republic of Moldova and Western Europe. It replaces scattered Facebook groups and ad-hoc WhatsApp threads with a searchable directory of trusted carriers, their routes, and their schedules — so sending a parcel home becomes a matter of minutes, not days of phone calls.",
  "slogan": "Connecting people, places, and stories — built for the Moldovan diaspora.",
